channel.description:
[B]Purpose:[/B] Adding Auto Updater to your client, that checks , if there is new version, and if there is really, it will download too


this updater downloads your client to your root folder of your client and replaces all old files in that folder.
This updater extract your client.zip, that client has downloaded, so you dont have to worry.

[B]Difficulty:[/B] 2/10

[B]Tested On:[/B] Project Fubergen clients since v4

[B]Assumed Knowledge:[/B] Copy and Paste
Classes Modified: client.java, Gui.java



